data.description: Wonderful ranch style home in a great location and neighborhood in town on a paved road! Fenced back yard with garden and fruit trees, plus a projector screen for movie nights. Landscaped in front and back. Sprinklers. Front covered porch. Back patio. Attached 2 car garage with large driveway in a cul-de-sac. Built in china cabinet in dining room. Living room features vaulted ceilings. Master bathroom has heated floors. Office/Den. Bonus room with backyard access. Grab this one quick!
